      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MANDOLIN STORM (5) slotted in just off the lead from the wide box before lifting strongly to score (22.80) at this track in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 over 400m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. One of the key runners again. SNOWBALL ONE (1) could manage only fourth at this track last time but turned heads when clocking a swift 22.16 over 390m at Warrnambool the start prior. Must include on winning run two back. STAR REBEL (4) finished well back at this track last time when a 9 length eighth (23.09) but scored five back at The Meadows (30.33). Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Can do much better this time. TINKER DOT (8) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
